name: SONOfSHIB
description: Through his years as a puppy, he faced many battles trying to prove himself. With each battle- came growth and scars that made him stronger and different from the world. Yet, he still maintained his moral code and positive view. Undeterred, his desire to reach his father grew even stronger, as the little one's community resiliently stood beside him. Now, his army's loyalty has never been higher. The difference...He is no longer that small puppy anymore - he is now--- the Son Of Shib
